(3, 'Introduction', NULL, '<div style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 100%; text-align: left;" align="justify"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" vspace="9" /></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 100%; text-align: left;" align="justify"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Java is a&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>programming language</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">&nbsp;and a&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>platform</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">.</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 100%; text-align: left;" align="justify"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Java is a high level, robust, secured and object-oriented programming language.</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 100%; text-align: left;" align="justify"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Platform</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Verdana,serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">: Any hardware or software environment in which a program runs, is known as a platform. Sin